OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776355854
OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's Executive has
OL,7,Fagreed to fund an additional #19.2
OL,8,Fmillion to go towards helping low-
OL,9,Fincome households with rising fuel
OL,10,Fcosts.
OL,12,FThe decision was agreed during a
OL,13,Fmeeting on Thursday, and comes on top
OL,14,Fof the #17.2 million of support from
OL,15,Fthe UK Government which was announced
OL,16,Flast month.
OL,18,FThe scheme will mean 300,000 low-
OL,19,Fincome families will receive #100 fuel
OL,20,Fvouchers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
