PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776355854
OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FThe new measures will mean eligible
OL,7,Fhouseholds will be able to apply for a
OL,8,F#100 prepaid card that can be used at
OL,9,Fhome heating oil suppliers.
OL,11,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,12,FPengelly said: "It will make a
OL,13,Fdifference, but it will not solve the
OL,14,Fproblem."
OL,16,FShe and First Minister Michelle
OL,17,FO'Neill called on Sir Keir Starmer to
OL,18,Fmeet with the Executive.
OL,26,@tD@POUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
