OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776355854
OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FMichelle O'Neill said the budget for
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland was "at breaking
OL,8,Fpoint" and the "picture that was
OL,9,Fpainted by all ministers today when it
OL,10,Fcomes to delivery of public services
OL,11,Fis stark".
OL,26,@oD@VOUpD@FO]pD@POUsD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
