PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776355854
OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FMs O'Neill continued: "We make a
OL,7,Fdirect appeal to the British Prime
OL,8,FMinister to meet with us in a cross-
OL,9,Fparty delegation, because the budget
OL,10,Frealities that we face are so
OL,11,Fchallenging and so dire and so
OL,12,Fdifficult that he needs to listen to
OL,13,Fthe concerns that all of us are
OL,14,Fexpressing on behalf of the people
OL,15,Fthat we collectively serve."
OL,17,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,18,FPengelly said that the people of
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland "cannot wait".
OL,26,@nD@WOUwD@\O]{D@ROU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
