OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776355854
OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FHe said the income threshold is based
OL,7,Fon the national minimum wage, "aligns
OL,8,Fwith that of my department's
OL,9,Fdiscretionary support scheme" and
OL,10,F"represents a fair assessment of where
OL,11,Fthe available funding can be directed".
OL,13,FPensioners will be eligible to apply
OL,14,Fif they are not in receipt of Pension
OL,15,FCredit or if they have an income above
OL,16,F30,000.
OL,18,FOnly one voucher will be available per
OL,19,Fhousehold and will be for oil
OL,20,Fcustomers "at this time".
OL,26,@oD@_OUqD@]O]rD@AOUsD@fO]|D@KOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
