PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776355854
OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FMr Lyons said roughly two thirds of
OL,7,Fhouseholds, around 500,000 homes, in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland rely on heating oil
OL,9,Fand recent price increases of "nearly
OL,10,F100%" have been "punishing".
OL,12,FHe acknowledged there has been
OL,13,Fcriticism of "how long it has taken
OL,14,Ffor us to progress this" adding "it
OL,15,Fwas important that we brought forward
OL,16,Fsomething that would actually help,
OL,17,Fthat was of sufficient scale, that
OL,18,Fwould actually provide help to those
OL,19,Fwho need it."
OL,26,@qD@_OUrD@EO]rD@QOUrD@[O]uD@NOUvD@XO]vD@
OL,26,AaOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
