OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FMr Lyons said he wanted to "manage
OL,7,Fexpectations" and said it would "take
OL,8,Ftime to implement".
OL,10,FHe said: "We need to make sure that we
OL,11,Fhave the legislation in place, that we
OL,12,Fhave the mechanism of delivery in
OL,13,Fplace, and that we ensure that the
OL,14,Feligibility checks are able to be
OL,15,Fcarried out."
OL,26,@nD@\OUoD@MO]oD@aOUpD@RO]rD@JOUwD@MO]
