OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FMs Little-Pengelly said the Executive
OL,7,F"will have more to say in the coming
OL,8,Fweeks in terms of discounts to
OL,9,Felectricity customers, because
OL,10,Fobviously our Economy Minister has
OL,11,Fbeen working on that for some time".
OL,13,FShe also said the Infrastructure
OL,14,FMinister spoke about "freezing
OL,15,Ftransport fares" on Wednesday, adding:
OL,16,F"That's ultimately about giving people
OL,17,Fchoice, because if you can't put fuel
OL,18,Fin your car, you may choose to take
OL,19,Fpublic transport."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@cO]vD@VOUwD@PO]xD@AOU{D@RO]
