OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FThe First Minister Michelle O'Neill
OL,7,Fsaid the Northern Ireland Executive
OL,8,Fwants to meet with British Prime
OL,9,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer about
OL,10,F"stark" budgetary issues.
OL,12,FMs O'Neill said the budget for
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland was "at breaking
OL,14,Fpoint" and the "picture that was
OL,15,Fpainted by all ministers today when it
OL,16,Fcomes to delivery of public services
OL,17,Fis stark".
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@GO]uD@VOUvD@FO]vD@POUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
