OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1776355854
OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,F"Political choices being made in
OL,7,FLondon are creating a really difficult
OL,8,Fatmosphere for our Executive to be
OL,9,Fable to work with," she said.
OL,11,F"We have had invited Hilary Benn, the
OL,12,FSecretary of State, along today ` he
OL,13,Fcouldn't make it (because of) diary
OL,14,Farrangements, apparently.
OL,16,F"However, we as an Executive have
OL,17,Ftoday decided that we want to meet
OL,18,Fwith Keir Starmer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@SO]sD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
