OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,F"We make a direct appeal to the
OL,7,FBritish Prime Minister to meet with us
OL,8,Fin a cross-party delegation, because
OL,9,Fthe budget realities that we face are
OL,10,Fso challenging and so dire and so
OL,11,Fdifficult that he needs to listen to
OL,12,Fthe concerns that all of us are
OL,13,Fexpressing on behalf of the people
OL,14,Fthat we collectively serve."
OL,16,FDeputy First Minister Emma Little-
OL,17,FPengelly said that the people of
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland "cannot wait".
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@\O]zD@ROUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
