OL,3,CNI budget is at 'breaking point' says
OL,4,CFirst Minister
OL,6,FShe said the Executive had decided to
OL,7,Fcall on Sir Keir "to act and to act
OL,8,Fnow", because the UK Government has
OL,9,F"the tools, it has the responsibility,
OL,10,Fand this is the moment to use both".
OL,12,F"Our message to the Prime Minister is
OL,13,Fsimple: this cannot wait. People
OL,14,Fcannot wait," she said.
OL,16,F"We need a comprehensive package of
OL,17,Fsupport, and we need it now, because
OL,18,Fbehind every statistic is a family and
OL,19,Fbehind every decision we make (there)
OL,20,Fmust be a determination to stand with
OL,21,Fthem.
